          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1687337713368-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> with the <strong>remaining berbere seasoning</strong>, the <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> drained green lentils </strong>and<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong></p><p>Cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add 450ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[900ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>,<strong> tomato paste </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
